
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>

<head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8 '>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'>
    <title>Quarantine Thoughts</title>
    <link href='style.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway&display=swap' rel='stylesheet'>
    <script src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.js'
        integrity='sha256-WpOohJOqMqqyKL9FccASB9O0KwACQJpFTUBLTYOVvVU=' crossorigin='anonymous'></script>
    <script src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/4db72034b4.js' crossorigin='anonymous'></script>
    <script src="app.js"></script>
</head>

<body id='home'>
    <header>
        <i class='fas fa-biohazard'><% ejsTitle %></i>
        <nav class='navbar-container'>
            <ul class='navbar'>
                <li>
                    <a href='#home'>Form</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href='#post-heading'>Posts</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <!--SUBMISSION FORM-->
        <h1 class='heading'>Send us your thoughts</h1>
        <form class='form-container' id='form' method="post" action="http://localhost:8000/submission">
            <div class='input-container'>
                <input type='text' name='title' id='title' class='input' placeholder='Title'>
            </div>
            <div class='input-container'>
                <textarea name='message' id='message' maxlength='255' class='input' placeholder='Your message'
                    rows='5'></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class='input-container'>
                <input type='text' name='gif' id='gif' class='input' placeholder='Link your favorite GIF!'>
            </div>
            <div class='input-container' id='submit'>
                <input type='submit' name='submit' class='submit' value='Post'>
            </div>
        </form>
        <h1 class='heading' id="post-heading">All Posts</h1>
        <!--5 POSTS-->
        <section id='posts'>
            <!--POST-->
            <div class='post-container' id="post-container1">
                <div class='post-title posts' id="post-title1">Feeling really sad</div>
                <div class='post-content'>
                    <div class='post-message posts' id="post-message1">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
                        adipiscing elit. In sit amet massa consequat ligula elementum vulputate. Sed consectetur risus
                        et molestie iaculis. Sed maximus mauris quis libero bibendum, sed pharetra odio venenatis.
                        Aliquam justo tortor, malesuada sed ipsum sit amet, volutpat porta tellus. Nulla vestibulum
                        imperdiet sapien venenatis pharetra. Donec orci odio, varius ac erat in, faucibus aliquet purus.
                        Nulla facilisi.
                    </div>
                    <div class='post-emoji posts dropdown'>
                        <img src="https://emojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/thumbs/160/facebook/230/slightly-smiling-face_1f642.png"
                            alt="smily emoji" class="post-emoji emoji-icon">
                        <div class="dropdown-content">
                            <a href="http://localhost:8000" id="post-emoji1-1">
                                <img src="https://emojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/thumbs/160/facebook/230/fire_1f525.png"
                                    alt="emoji fire" class="post-emoji second-emoji">
                            </a>
                            <span class="span" id="span1-1">1</span>
                            <a href="http://localhost:8000" id="post-emoji1-2">
                                <img src="https://slack-imgs.com/?c=1&o1=ro&url=https%3A%2F%2Femojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fthumbs%2F160%2Ffacebook%2F230%2Floudly-crying-face_1f62d.png"
                                    alt="crying emoji" class="post-emoji">
                            </a>
                            <span class="span" id="span1-2">1</span>
                            <a href="http://localhost:8000" id="post-emoji1-3">
                                <img src="https://slack-imgs.com/?c=1&o1=ro&url=https%3A%2F%2Femojipedia-us.s3.dualstack.us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fthumbs%2F160%2Ffacebook%2F230%2Fsmiling-face-with-open-mouth-and-smiling-eyes_1f604.png"
                                    alt="crying emoji" class="post-emoji">
                            </a>
                            <span class="span" id="span1-3">1</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='post-gif posts'>
                    <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/mCRJDo24UvJMA/giphy.gif" alt="gif image" class="gif-img"
                        id="post-gif1">
                </div>
                <!--COMMENT SECTION-->
                <div class='post-comments posts'></div>
                <div class='input-comment-container posts'>
                    <form class='form-comments'>
                        <textarea class='input-comment' rows='3' placeholder='Write a comment'
                            id='textarea1'></textarea>
                        <div id='comment1'>
                            <input type='submit' name='submit-comment' class="submit-comment" value='Send'>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <!--COMMENTS-->
                    <div id="commentSection1">
                        <div class='display-comment posts' id="display-comment1-1"></div>
                        <div class='display-comment posts' id="display-comment1-2"></div>
                        <div class='display-comment posts' id="display-comment1-3"></div>
                        <div class='display-comment posts' id="display-comment1-4"></div>
                        <div class='display-comment posts' id="display-comment1-5"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
